  "text": [
    {
      "startMs": 2000,
      "endMs": 3579,
      "text": "the envelope was thin.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 3753,
      "endMs": 5785,
      "text": "darnell turned it over once in his hands",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 5855,
      "endMs": 7399,
      "text": "like it might be heavier from the other",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 7457,
      "endMs": 9152,
      "text": "side. it was not.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 9326,
      "endMs": 11567,
      "text": "he had poured forty-one days into the conner",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 11636,
      "endMs": 12600,
      "text": "avenue job.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 12925,
      "endMs": 15990,
      "text": "forty-one days of iron in january, fingers that",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 16048,
      "endMs": 18323,
      "text": "cracked and bled before eight in the morning,",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 18707,
      "endMs": 21110,
      "text": "boots that never fully dried.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 21806,
      "endMs": 23525,
      "text": "he knew the number in that envelope the",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 23571,
      "endMs": 25649,
      "text": "way a man knows the distance between two",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 25765,
      "endMs": 28482,
      "text": "points he has walked a thousand times.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 29086,
      "endMs": 31907,
      "text": "and what he found inside was not that",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 32023,
      "endMs": 35448,
      "text": "number. the foreman's name was pruitt.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 36563,
      "endMs": 37991,
      "text": "he ran the trailer office at the south",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 38037,
      "endMs": 39883,
      "text": "end of the lot, a dented aluminum box",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 39941,
      "endMs": 42263,
      "text": "that smelled of burnt coffee and old paper.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 43076,
      "endMs": 45282,
      "text": "darnell walked to it without hurrying.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 45886,
      "endMs": 48115,
      "text": "pruitt was at his desk when darnell opened",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 48138,
      "endMs": 49009,
      "text": "the door.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 49612,
      "endMs": 50727,
      "text": "he did not look up.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 51621,
      "endMs": 54489,
      "text": "there's three hundred short, darnell said.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 55255,
      "endMs": 57287,
      "text": "pruitt tapped something into his keyboard.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 58053,
      "endMs": 59075,
      "text": "accounting error.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 59434,
      "endMs": 60921,
      "text": "we'll sort it next cycle.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 61815,
      "endMs": 63684,
      "text": "darnell set the envelope flat on the desk",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 63754,
      "endMs": 64554,
      "text": "between them.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 65379,
      "endMs": 67062,
      "text": "there is no next cycle.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 68003,
      "endMs": 70673,
      "text": "last day was yesterday.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 71613,
      "endMs": 72937,
      "text": "pruitt looked up then.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 73320,
      "endMs": 75433,
      "text": "his eyes were small and patient the way",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 75480,
      "endMs": 77047,
      "text": "a man's eyes get when he has made",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 77093,
      "endMs": 78672,
      "text": "other men wait before.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 79624,
      "endMs": 81018,
      "text": "i said we'll sort it.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 81447,
      "endMs": 83003,
      "text": "darnell did not raise his voice.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 83026,
      "endMs": 84246,
      "text": "he had no need to.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 84687,
      "endMs": 87311,
      "text": "that money was mine the hour i earned",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 87380,
      "endMs": 90410,
      "text": "it. nothing you do between now and whenever",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 90468,
      "endMs": 91629,
      "text": "changes that.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 92233,
      "endMs": 93905,
      "text": "i'm not asking for a favor.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 94718,
      "endMs": 96691,
      "text": "i'm not asking you for anything.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 97643,
      "endMs": 99153,
      "text": "he pulled out his phone and set it",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 99199,
      "endMs": 100465,
      "text": "beside the envelope.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 101162,
      "endMs": 103449,
      "text": "he dialed the labor board number he had",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 103484,
      "endMs": 105515,
      "text": "looked up the night before, not hoping he",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 105550,
      "endMs": 107164,
      "text": "would need it but knowing the way a",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 107222,
      "endMs": 110090,
      "text": "carpenter knows which tool is in which pocket.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 111042,
      "endMs": 112528,
      "text": "pruitt watched him.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 113480,
      "endMs": 116510,
      "text": "the line rang twice and a woman answered",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 116835,
      "endMs": 119285,
      "text": "and darnell gave her his name and the",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 119332,
      "endMs": 122606,
      "text": "company name and the address of the site.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 123720,
      "endMs": 125218,
      "text": "he spoke quietly.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 126031,
      "endMs": 127598,
      "text": "he did not look at pruitt while he",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 127644,
      "endMs": 130907,
      "text": "spoke. he looked out the trailer's single window",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 130965,
      "endMs": 133357,
      "text": "at the steel skeleton rising against the white",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 133403,
      "endMs": 135876,
      "text": "detroit sky, the structure he had helped lift",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 135899,
      "endMs": 138732,
      "text": "from nothing, bolt by bolt in the cold.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 139545,
      "endMs": 141286,
      "text": "when he hung up he picked up the",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 141333,
      "endMs": 143690,
      "text": "envelope and folded it into his jacket pocket.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 144293,
      "endMs": 146697,
      "text": "you just made this complicated, pruitt said.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 147510,
      "endMs": 149007,
      "text": "no, darnell said.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 149332,
      "endMs": 150261,
      "text": "you did that.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 150702,
      "endMs": 152119,
      "text": "i only made it certain.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 153233,
      "endMs": 154580,
      "text": "he stepped out of the trailer and the",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 154638,
      "endMs": 156937,
      "text": "cold hit him clean and hard.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 157448,
      "endMs": 158829,
      "text": "snow was coming.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 159154,
      "endMs": 160641,
      "text": "he could smell it the way you smell",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 160757,
      "endMs": 162359,
      "text": "iron before it rusts.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 163473,
      "endMs": 164913,
      "text": "he walked to his truck at the far",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 164982,
      "endMs": 166956,
      "text": "end of the lot, past the frozen mud",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 167037,
      "endMs": 171333,
      "text": "ruts, past the scrap pile, past the other",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 171391,
      "endMs": 174468,
      "text": "men who looked at him and looked away.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 175768,
      "endMs": 177823,
      "text": "he sat in the cab and did not",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 177881,
      "endMs": 179797,
      "text": "start the engine right away.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 180493,
      "endMs": 182780,
      "text": "he pressed his palms flat against the steering",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 182826,
      "endMs": 184545,
      "text": "wheel and looked at the scar on his",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 184626,
      "endMs": 187134,
      "text": "left knuckle from a cable that had slipped",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 187169,
      "endMs": 189003,
      "text": "in february two years back.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 189955,
      "endMs": 191766,
      "text": "he had kept working that day.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 192207,
      "endMs": 194053,
      "text": "he had kept working because the work was",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 194123,
      "endMs": 196294,
      "text": "his and the wage that followed it was",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 196364,
      "endMs": 200265,
      "text": "his and no man's slow-rolling indifference could reach",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 200323,
      "endMs": 204027,
      "text": "back into those forty-one days and unmake them.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 205327,
      "endMs": 206836,
      "text": "the snow started.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 207161,
      "endMs": 210133,
      "text": "small flakes first, then heavier ones that stuck",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 210192,
      "endMs": 211805,
      "text": "to the windshield and held.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 212409,
      "endMs": 213721,
      "text": "he started the truck.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 214325,
      "endMs": 216345,
      "text": "the heater groaned to life.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 216519,
      "endMs": 218644,
      "text": "he pulled out of the lot and onto",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 218714,
      "endMs": 222092,
      "text": "conner avenue heading north and did not look",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 222150,
      "endMs": 223915,
      "text": "in the rearview mirror once.",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 224356,
      "endMs": 226423,
      "text": "the city spread out ahead of him gray",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 226492,
      "endMs": 229395,
      "text": "and cold and indifferent as it always had",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 229464,
      "endMs": 232204,
      "text": "been. and he drove through it like a",
      "position": "bottom"
    },
    {
      "startMs": 232274,
      "endMs": 234619,
      "text": "man who had already settled his accounts.",
      "position": "bottom"
    }
  ],
  "audio": [
    {
      "startMs": 2000,
      "endMs": 234619,
      "audioUrl": "voice"
    }
  ]
}